          "ev-004",
          "ev-005"
        ],
        "tx_hashes": []
      },
      {
        "title": "Step 2",
        "detail": "Attacker executes a preparation transaction (0x43aa42d2f11afe42832a9619bc8066dfb83a921798b91eaf9d0345dd27dcfb06) to set up the attack, potentially interacting with liquidity pools and the Paribus protocol contracts.",
        "evidence_refs": [
          "ev-008",
          "ev-033"
        ],
        "tx_hashes": []
      },
      {
        "title": "Step 3",
        "detail": "Attacker performs price manipulation by executing swaps through what appears to be a Uniswap V3 router (0xE592427A0AEce92De3Edee1F18E0157C05861564) to artificially inflate the price of a collateral asset used by Paribus.",
        "evidence_refs": [
          "ev-016",
          "ev-010",
          "ev-015"
        ],
        "tx_hashes": []
      },
      {
        "title": "Step 4",
        "detail": "Using the manipulated price, attacker interacts with Paribus protocol contracts (including 0x794a61358D6845594F94dc1DB02A252b5b4814aD and 0x56190CAC88b8D4b5D5Ed668ef81828913932e7Ed) to deposit artificially valued collateral and borrow or withdraw assets at a favorable rate.",
        "evidence_refs": [
          "ev-014",
          "ev-010",
          "ev-017"
        ],
        "tx_hashes": []
      },
      {
        "title": "Step 5",
